    Example: Nuclear potential

```C++
    double Z = 1.0;                 // Hydrogen nuclear charge
    auto f = [Z] (const double *r) -> double {
        double R = sqrt(r[0]*r[0] + r[1]*r[1] + r[2]*r[2]);
        return Z/R;
    }
```
